Job Title: CONSUMER & MARKET KNOWLEDGE – ADVANCED COMMERCIAL ANALYTICS SENIOR MANAGER (Experienced)
Job Description:
Are you energized by solving tough business problems, wrangling massive datasets, and developing clever code to generate insight from diverse sources of data? Are you curious?

If so, then a role in the Consumer & Market Knowledge (CMK) Commercial Analytics organization is for you! In CMK, we combine analytics and data science techniques to directly influence business strategy, product design, pricing, media investments, retail, go to market strategy … and much more. We use our data and boundless curiosity to discover what consumers want, why they want it, and how we can influence them through immersive exploration and in-depth analysis. We use internal and external data sources accessed via our Hadoop cluster to build predictive and explanatory models that enable insights into how our consumers, markets, and retailers behave.

Your role in CMK will involve building reproducible code, predictive models, analytics, storytelling, visualizations, and engaging presentations that facilitate a deep understanding of consumer and shopper behaviors. Your key to success will be your ability to integrate exploratory data analysis, model building, model optimization and model production to deliver insights that drive the business.

So, here’s your opportunity! We’re looking for hardworking and data driven individuals. Join CMK and help us anticipate what consumers want and to enable the business.
